5A.  (1)  Subject to sections 3 and 5, the Bank shall set out the terms
and conditions of any instrument to be issued.
(2)  The terms and conditions of an instruments shall include the
following:
(a) amount;
(b) issue date;
(c) maturity date;
(d) return;
(e) repayment of investment; and
(f) any other terms and conditions as the Bank deems fit.
